{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "第七回《沈太君的气派》讲述了萧十一郎与风四娘乔装潜入沈家庄的故事。沈家庄大明湖边，沈太君主持门户，各方武林人士齐聚：万重山接待宾客，厉刚因大开碑手名扬天下，徐青藤为世袭杭州将军。赵无极与连城璧到来后，透露宝刀流星在护送途中被风四娘与萧十一郎夺走，沈太君对此事洞若观火。沈太君以幽默睿智的言辞震慑全场，化解厉刚与杨开泰的冲突。萧十一郎与风四娘在后园密谈真刀假刀之谜，杨开泰对风四娘一片痴心，风四娘被其真诚感动。萧十一郎悄然离去，留下字条劝风四娘嫁给杨开泰，独自在星空下踽踽独行，感叹人生如鞭子般驱赶着他不断前行。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "厉兄近来可曾到少林去过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "这位冯兄是阁下的朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "他真的姓冯？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "阁下若认为我们不姓冯，那么我们应该姓什么呢？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位无论姓什么，都与厉某无关，只不过厉某生平最见不得藏头露尾，改名换姓之辈，若是见到，就绝不肯放过。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chong_shan",
      "speaker_name": "万重山",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "厉兄为人之刚正，是大家都知道的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_teng",
      "speaker_name": "徐青藤",
      "listener": "char_wan_chong_shan",
      "text": "白水兄呢？为何还没有来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chong_shan",
      "speaker_name": "万重山",
      "listener": "char_xu_qing_teng",
      "text": "白水兄已在峨嵋金顶剃度，这次只怕是不会来的了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_teng",
      "speaker_name": "徐青藤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他怎会如此想不开？其中莫非还有什么隐情么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论他是为了什么，都大大的不该，朱家世代单传，只有他这一个独子，他却出家做了和尚；常言道：不孝有三，无后为大。亏他还念过几天书，竟连这句话都忘了，我若见了他……哼。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "你看这人多奇怪，什么人的闲事他都要来管管。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我就是喜欢管闲事，你不服？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "厉兄莫要忘了，他是我的朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "是你的朋友又怎样？厉某今日就要教训教训你这朋友。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "好好好，你……你……你不妨先来教训教训我吧。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们到这里来，是想来打架的么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_xu_qing_teng",
      "text": "徐青藤，你帽子上这粒珍珠可真不错呀，但你将它钉在帽子上，岂非太可惜了吗？你为什么不将它挂在鼻子上呢？也好让别人看得更清楚些。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_liu_se_qing",
      "text": "几年不见，你剑法想必又精进了吧？天下大概已没有人能比得上你了吧！其实你外号应该叫做天下第一剑才对，至少你身上挂的这把剑比别人的都漂亮得多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "小侄方才一时无礼，还求太夫人恕罪。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "什么，你说什么？我听不见呀。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "小……小侄方才无……无礼……",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "哦——原来你是说没有带礼物来呀，那有什么关系，反正我知道你是个小气鬼，连自己都舍不得吃，舍不得穿，怎么会送礼给别人？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "晚辈方才也并未想和杨兄打架，只不过这两人……",
      "tone": "辩解",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "什么？你说这两人想打架？不会的，这两人看来都是好孩子，怎么会在我这里打架，只有那种没规矩的野孩子才会在这里吹胡子、瞪眼睛，你说是吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "太夫人说的是。",
      "tone": "顺从",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这地方本来客人还不少，可是自从璧君出了嫁之后，就已有很久没这么热闹过了，我这才明白，原来那些人并不是来看我这老太婆的，但今天你们若也想来看看我们那位大美人儿，只怕就难免要失望。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们那位大丫头今天可不能见客，她有病。",
      "tone": "关切",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "有病？什么病？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "傻孩子，你着急什么？她若真的有病，我还会这么开心？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "告诉你，她不是有病，是有喜。但你可千万不能说是我说的，免得那丫头又怪我老婆子多嘴。",
      "tone": "神秘",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "你开心什么？孩子又不是你的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "晚辈来迟，有劳太夫人久候，恕罪恕罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "没关系，来迟了总比不来的好，是吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "屠啸天、海灵子和那老鹰王呢？他们为什么不来？难道没有脸来见我？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "他们的确无颜来见太夫人……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "刀丢了，是吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "刀丢了倒没关系，只怕连人也丢了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "晚辈实也无颜来见太夫人，只不过……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你用不着解释，我也知道这件事责任绝不在你，有老鹰王和你们在一起，他一定会抢着要带那把刀，所以刀一定是在他手里丢了的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "纵然如此，晚辈亦难辞疏忽之罪，若不能将刀夺回，晚辈是再也无颜见武林同道的了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "能自那老鹰王手里将刀夺去的人，世上倒也没几个，夺刀的人是谁呀？那人的本领不小吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "风四娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "风四娘？……这名字我倒也听说过，听说她手上功夫也有两下子，但就凭她那两下子，只怕还夺不走老鹰王手里的刀吧！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "她自然还有个帮手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "萧十一郎！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧十一郎，萧十一郎……最近我怎么总是听到这人的名字，好像天下的坏事都被他一人做尽了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我老婆子倒真想见见这个人，一个人就能做出这么多坏事来，倒也不容易。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "此人不除，江湖难安！晚辈迟早总有一日提他的首级来见太夫人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_xu_qing_teng",
      "text": "徐青藤，你想不想要萧十一郎的头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_qing_teng",
      "speaker_name": "徐青藤",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "厉兄说的不错，此人不除，江湖难安……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_liu_se_qing",
      "text": "柳色青，你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_se_qing",
      "speaker_name": "柳色青",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "晚辈久已想与此人一较高低。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你这孩子什么都好，就是太不爱说话了……你们信不信，他到我这里来了半个月，我还没有听他说过十句话。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "你想说什么？说呀，难道你也想学他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "晚辈总觉得有时不说话反比说话好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "那么你呢？你想不想杀萧十一郎？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "此人恶名四溢，无论谁能除去此人，都可名扬天下，晚辈自然也有这意思，只不过……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "只不过怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "text": "晚辈只怕还不是他的敌手。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "好，还是你这孩子说话老实，我老婆子就喜欢这种规规矩矩，本本分分的人，只可惜我没有第二个孙女儿嫁给你。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_tai_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈太君",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "你看，有这么多人都想要萧十一郎的头，你想提他的头来见我，只怕还不大容易吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你感觉如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我开心极了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "开心？你还觉得开心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我还不知道我的头如此值钱，否则只怕也早就送进当铺了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们夺到的明明是假刀，但他们丢的却偏偏是真刀，你说这件事奇怪不奇怪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不奇怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不奇怪？你知道真刀到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "真刀……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "你是不是要我谢谢你？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我……我没有这意思。",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "我本来是应该谢谢你，你方才若说出我是风四娘，那些人一定不会放过我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我为什么要……要说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "他们不是说我就是那偷刀的贼么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我知道你不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为……因为……我相信你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "你为什么相信我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "没有为什么，我就是……就是相信你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "你真是个好人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我……我并不太好，我……我也不太坏，我……",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "你真是个君子，可也真是个呆子……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "他的人呢，你看见他到哪里去了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "他……我堂弟，你没有看见他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "没……没有。",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "你难道是瞎子？他那么大一个人你会看不见？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我……我真的没看见，我只……只看见你……",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "你呀，你真是个呆子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这混账，这畜生，简直不是人生父母养的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他不是你堂弟吗？你怎么能这样子骂他！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "谁说他是我堂弟，你活见了鬼吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "杨开泰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他不是你堂弟是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_yang_kai_tai",
      "text": "他……他……他也是个呆子！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    }
